DVD drive<br />
SVGA (1024&#215;768) or higher resolution monitor<br />
Internet connection<br />
Windows Installer Service 4.5; .NET 4.0<br />
1 GB system memory</p>
<p>Processor speed for Windows® XP<br />
1.0 GHz Pentium® IV processor (or equivalent)<br />
Processor speed for Windows Vista®, Windows 7, or Windows 8<br />
1.8 GHz Pentium IV processor (or equivalent)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
