Lotus Notes® 8.0 and 8.5<br />
Internet Mail SMTP/POP3<br />
Microsoft Internet Explorer® 7.02, 8.02, 9.02, 10.02<br />
Adobe® Reader® 6.0, 7.0 and 10.x<br />
Citrix® software using Citrix XenApp® 5.0 and 6.0</td>
